      <title>特鲁多考虑实施点名羞辱政策，遏制虐待外国工人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/trudeau-mulls-name-and-shame-policy-to-curb-foreign-worker-abuse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府正在考虑进行改革，以打击虐待临时外国工人的行为——公开点名违反加拿大劳动法规的企业经理或业主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/trudeau-mulls-name-and-shame-policy-to-curb-foreign-worker-abuse</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 15:53:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
